cast.overview: On the first day at his new school, Cameron instantly falls for Bianca, the gorgeous girl of his dreams. The only problem is that Bianca is forbidden to date until her ill-tempered, completely un-dateable older sister Kat goes out, too. In an attempt to solve his problem, Cameron singles out the only guy who could possibly be a match for Kat: a mysterious bad boy with a nasty reputation of his own.
cast.title: 10 Things I Hate About You

details.biography: Quinn Maixner was born on May 20, 1979 in Newberg, Oregon, USA. He was an actor, known for 10 Things I Hate About You (1999). He died on July 3, 2021.
details.name: Quinn Maixner
